{"tid":1403983,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[圍爐]有無人試過去完camp好唔開心","createTime":"2019-08-04T01:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T19:26:52.000Z","uid":246742,"like":134,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"daa5ae7c122bab18685d4ec5eb049f6d854f9d54","tid":1403983,"uid":246742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:40:42.000Z","msg":"introvert忍唔住想開post<br />\n去完camp發現識唔到人好灰<br />\n個camp2日一夜 咁去之前同自己組員都見過幾次面<br />\n食飯食糖水咁 相處融恰<br />\n本身個人唔多野講  所以都預左去camp會有啲辛苦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺幾個月前，曾經同鐘意的人講自己單身<br />\n佢答左我一句:去多啲活動囉<br />\n所以促成左我參加呢個camp<br />\n其實我只是一個想識多啲朋友的女仔<br />\n所以一直對所有人都好nice<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平時我都有化下妝做下運動keep好自己 <br />\n成個camp過程都有好努力去融入<br />\n對比之下 都是唔夠其他人多野講<br />\n無論男女 都係會圍住識yo的靚仔靚女<br />\n原來大家性格咁大分別 想融入真是好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本身家母身體唔係咁好  返到屋企見到佢為我準備好哂晚飯同熱湯  <br />\n知我無訓教又叮囑我小心身體<br />\n個心即刻好後悔自己有一晚無留喺屋企好好陪佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢家打哂出來個心好似舒服啲咁<br />\n預左咁長會無人睇 如果你睇到呢到 好多謝你願意睇我打嘅野<br />\n有無人可以傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4721222f4e266c4b11cccb80e115b53da47acc","tid":1403983,"uid":127416,"like":59,"dislike":3,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:42:56.000Z","msg":"我覺得妳唸太多嘢"},{"pid":"ac58d5788200f7abfbc08a8b7af7084ace3565a8","tid":1403983,"uid":76404,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:50:52.000Z","msg":"絲打好乖，我都試過因爲冇陪屋企人而內疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97beb2cb4e3a02f3c5af625f6e7801f1b2d9d90","tid":1403983,"uid":71175,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:55:07.000Z","msg":"一堆年青男女 Ocmap <br />\n<br />\n緊係圍住靚仔靚女<br />\n<br />\n要識男仔 唔駛急住o camp 識<br />\n<br />\n仲有幾年時間讀書"},{"pid":"e91769540d924d5c1994be4ee6c3b5644eade9ab","tid":1403983,"uid":87520,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd07929de56b590fb1c2ba88b05911961144e11b","tid":1403983,"uid":240960,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:03:45.000Z","msg":"從來都唔需要強求去揾朋友<br />\n你有你自己既態度自然有人欣賞你"},{"pid":"72104c619662c5c1761c3a03b91da25589f9e377","tid":1403983,"uid":248834,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:08:23.000Z","msg":"樣衰無計"},{"pid":"ffb977dd19b56159d0e31e40d9d33e34c031a816","tid":1403983,"uid":173973,"like":38,"dislike":3,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:34:18.000Z","msg":"我見d內向妹多數去camp個樣都係黑口黑面 又唔出聲 點同你溝通 轉過頭又想連登話大家淨係圍住靚仔靚女 真係好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30130e5af3dbceccab100392cb21dfd631bb1739","tid":1403983,"uid":246742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca4721222f4e266c4b11cccb80e115b53da47acc","tid":1403983,"uid":127416,"like":59,"dislike":3,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:42:56.000Z","msg":"我覺得妳唸太多嘢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:34:56.000Z","msg":"我都承認我係一個成日諗多左的人 <br />\n可能因為之後仲有一次camp要一齊喇～<br />\n所以出左camp仲諗緊<br />\n聽完你咁講 我嘗試focus返係其他野度 <br />\n咁諗個人會開心啲同輕鬆啲!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667bfb2a15321373236d62b1437ef6d027a5fc6b","tid":1403983,"uid":172306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:01:09.000Z","msg":"點解要改變自己性格？咁樣只會令自己辛苦"},{"pid":"63880c4fdc7e1f0be3351e50a68e11e09fdadfa1","tid":1403983,"uid":83904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:08:15.000Z","msg":"唔岩就唔岩 勉強都無用<br />\n做番自己鐘意既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總會搵到同自己志趣相投既人<br />\n<br />\n通常勉強埋堆最後都唔會開心"},{"pid":"c7fdcf35f7c491d003f591ba0a45a56f57aa5ee2","tid":1403983,"uid":127416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30130e5af3dbceccab100392cb21dfd631bb1739","tid":1403983,"uid":246742,"like":0,"dislike"