2,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:53:16.000Z","msg":"Camp定ocamp呀？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">話緊你班盲毛</span>"},{"pid":"c25f7621a3e78de7f3440062d5ff1eaeab4dab80","tid":1403983,"uid":48939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:18:31.000Z","msg":"好睇你咩目的 有人想上莊 有人只係想揾groupmate<br />\n咁係大學就係咁 你識主動外向一定著數好多 因為呢到唔係中學困住係同一班 佢地冇需要去就你 <br />\n但同時你都一樣可以揀唔理佢地 冇錯同啱 所以我覺得唔使唔開心 除非你想令自己更加外向 咁過程就一定辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51042dc2df207e6104825cf2ca1166c8c8e977f","tid":1403983,"uid":214479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:29:15.000Z","msg":"嘗試新既事物總會唔適應架啦 你估世界仔易做架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7af2a7c7271a2d41d5647f25236f63f0fb50be","tid":1403983,"uid":280696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:32:03.000Z","msg":"肯下決心試啲自己唔肯試既野已經好叻啦<br />\n<br />\nIntrovert 咪introvert <br />\n<br />\n慢慢接觸多啲人先會搵到人包容你架麻"},{"pid":"7bb6bfa132eaa47761444b5bcec05f87115843ec","tid":1403983,"uid":45848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f993717fa563db5024b740209ea1b8f669d00f10","tid":1403983,"uid":104502,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:13:01.000Z","msg":"唔靚嘅人 做咩都無用"},{"pid":"186e2946e13f5ae3fcc5f5cd066681f90ab20622","tid":1403983,"uid":87027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:18:53.000Z","msg":"絲打可以留tg？我都面對緊差不多問題<br />\n我都係絲"},{"pid":"5ef5d22d268ffee06a9a0d900e442334fb8c04ae","tid":1403983,"uid":199861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:56:32.000Z","msg":"聽日一齊去沙田行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大把人想識你"},{"pid":"1fa1f141a32bef4cb